55+ ACTIVE LIVING IN BEAUTIFUL SOUTHWEST, FLORIDA!
Located in sunny, coastal Palmetto, Florida, Country Lakes Villages offers everything one could ask for in a manufactured home community. With over 470 homes with in our two delightful active adult communities surrounded by tranquil lakes, splendid gardens, and lavish wildlife preserves, you will surely find a place to call your own.
We are just a short drive away from gorgeous beaches, only 5 miles from the Ellenton Premium Outlet shopping center, and surrounded by golf courses galore! At Country Lakes Villages it is possible to live in a lovely, country-like setting away from the hustle and bustle of city traffic but close to everything necessary.

Parks and Recreation
The Palmetto, Bradenton and Sarasota county areas have many beautiful parks to explore that are rich in water views and surrounded by the lush tropical nature. Whether you are looking for recreation or relaxation, there is a park that is perfect for you.
